  "title": "Cost Accountant (Manufacturing, Hands On Cost Accounting)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><ul><li><p>Manage and maintain <strong>full sets of accounts</strong>, including Accounts Receivable, Accounts Payable, General Ledger, and month-end and year-end closing</p></li><li><p>Perform comprehensive <strong>cost accounting functions</strong>, including standard costing, cost analysis, variance analysis, and inventory valuation</p></li><li><p>Monitor and analyze manufacturing costs, identify cost variances, and provide insights to improve cost efficiency and profitability</p></li><li><p>Prepare monthly management reports, financial statements, and supporting schedules</p></li><li><p>Work closely with operations and supply chain teams to ensure accurate cost capture and reporting</p></li><li><p>Support budgeting, forecasting, audit processes, and compliance with internal controls and accounting standards<br /></p><p><br /></p><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></h3><h3></h3><h3></h3><ul><li><p>Degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related discipline.</p></li><li><p>Minimum <strong>3–5 years of relevant accounting experience</strong>, with strong exposure to <strong>cost accounting</strong></p></li><li><p>Prior experience in a <strong>manufacturing environment is preferred</strong></p></li><li><p>Proven ability to handle <strong>full sets of accounts independently</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong analytical, organizational, and problem-solving skills</p></li><li><p>Proficient in accounting systems (Oracle NetSuite) and Microsoft Excel<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p><br /> </p><p>Interested applicants, please click on “<strong>Apply Now</strong>”. We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /> </p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /> </p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website <a href=\"http://www.trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.trustrecruit.com.sg</a>.</p><p><br /> </p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p><br /> </p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p><br /> </p><p>EA Personnel: Khor Khang Qin</p><p><br /> </p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R22109669</p>",
